verses.text: For \w the|strong="H5329"\w* choirmaster: \w To|strong="H5329"\w* \w the|strong="H5329"\w* tune \w of|strong="H4210"\w* “Do Not Destroy.” \w A|strong="H3068"\w* \w Psalm|strong="H4210"\w* \w of|strong="H4210"\w* Asaph. \w A|strong="H3068"\w* \w song|strong="H7892"\w*. We give thanks \w to|strong="H5329"\w* You, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God; \w we|strong="H3068"\w* give thanks, for Your Name is near. \w The|strong="H5329"\w* people declare Your wondrous works.
“When \w I|strong="H8034"\w* choose \w a|strong="H3068"\w* time, \w I|strong="H8034"\w* \w will|strong="H8034"\w* judge fairly.

\w When|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* earth \w and|strong="H3947"\w* \w all|strong="H3947"\w* \w its|strong="H3588"\w* dwellers quake, \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w who|strong="H3588"\w* bear \w up|strong="H3947"\w* \w its|strong="H3588"\w* pillars. Selah

\w I|strong="H3605"\w* say \w to|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* proud, ‘\w Do|strong="H3605"\w* not boast,’ \w and|strong="H3427"\w* \w to|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wicked, ‘\w Do|strong="H3605"\w* not lift \w up|strong="H3427"\w* \w your|strong="H3605"\w* horn.

Do not \w lift|strong="H7311"\w* \w up|strong="H7311"\w* \w your|strong="H7311"\w* \w horn|strong="H7161"\w* against heaven or speak \w with|strong="H7161"\w* \w an|strong="H7311"\w* outstretched neck.’”
\w For|strong="H7311"\w* \w exaltation|strong="H7311"\w* comes neither from east nor west, nor \w out|strong="H1696"\w* \w of|strong="H7161"\w* \w the|strong="H1696"\w* desert,

\w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H4161"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w who|strong="H3588"\w* judges; \w He|strong="H3588"\w* brings \w down|strong="H3588"\w* \w one|strong="H3808"\w* \w and|strong="H4057"\w* \w exalts|strong="H7311"\w* \w another|strong="H3808"\w*.

\w For|strong="H3588"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cup \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w in|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* hand \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, full \w of|strong="H8199"\w* foaming wine mixed \w with|strong="H8199"\w* spices. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* pours from \w His|strong="H3588"\w* cup, \w and|strong="H2088"\w* all \w the|strong="H3588"\w* wicked \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* earth drink \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w down|strong="H8213"\w* \w to|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* dregs.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* proclaim \w Him|strong="H3027"\w* \w forever|strong="H3605"\w*; \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* sing \w praise|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Jacob.

“\w All|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* horns \w of|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* wicked \w I|strong="H5046"\w* \w will|strong="H3290"\w* cut off, \w but|strong="H3290"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* horns \w of|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* righteous \w will|strong="H3290"\w* \w be|strong="H5769"\w* exalted.”
